{"tid":2136954,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"保皇黨網上聯署促押後選舉 每分鐘逾200人簽名","createTime":"2020-08-02T13:49:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-02T14:52:18.000Z","uid":240362,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"7cb39c44c7ce9bbcd8ed28947ccd25b802bdb503","tid":2136954,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T13:49:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200802/7L74NPCIICYNZRWAAJMWASOUTM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200802%2F7L74NPCIICYNZRWAAJMWASOUTM%2F&d=aFheyUS8Hi5o9a%2F4VMBAnVe0bVP%2BLlUkdLfYKyPPBhg%3D&h=f926b6dc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200802%2F7L74NPCIICYNZRWAAJMWASOUTM%2F&h=f9ce9460\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200802/7L74NPCIICYNZRWAAJMWASOUTM/</a><br />\n<br />\n前觀塘區議會主席陳振彬喺去年區選，敗於本土派素人李嘉達手下，結束20年觀塘區議員生涯後，搞咗個「全港抗疫連線」嘅組織出嚟，疫情爆發期間，不時派口罩緊箍藍絲支持，當然少不免為政府保駕護航。聯署網站至今日傍晚只運作咗約40幾小時，但已經有超過66萬人簽名，計落每分鐘都不停有成200幾人簽名。"},{"pid":"57cfb43b0f70d2777db740e0d689c46a70be66ad","tid":2136954,"uid":43062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T13:52:46.000Z","msg":"乜撚都依法依法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁多你支持做咩咁驚輸呀"},{"pid":"d6011c386a6307ae2079af95a46b8d1a19f0aeab","tid":2136954,"uid":156913,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T13:52:58.000Z","msg":"幫佢谷到過14億?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d41eb5ca061a9541e16a12ea305cf09838f8433","tid":2136954,"uid":66324,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"d6011c386a6307ae2079af95a46b8d1a19f0aeab","tid":2136954,"uid":156913,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T13:52:58.000Z","msg":"幫佢谷到過14億?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"re